Global Fuel Tank Vent Valve Market Insights
Fuel Tank Vent Valve Market size was valued at USD 0.95 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Fuel Tank Vent Valve Market Overview
The global fuel tank vent valve market has been experiencing steady growth due to the increasing demand for fuel efficiency and stringent emission regulations. As vehicles become more advanced with regards to fuel storage systems, vent valves play a critical role in ensuring that gas vapors are properly managed to prevent emissions. In 2023, the market was valued at approximately USD 1.8 billion and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030. The expansion of electric vehicles and technological advancements in valve designs are anticipated to further fuel market demand.

